name: INListCarsIntentResponseCode
desc: Constants that represent the status of a response.

items.name: case failure
items.desc: A response code that indicates you’re unable to retrieve a list of the user’s electric vehicles.

items.name: case failureRequiringAppLaunch
items.desc: A response code that indicates the system must launch your app before you can provide a list of the user’s electric vehicles.

items.name: case inProgress
items.desc: A response code that indicates you’re in the process of retrieving a list of the user’s electric vehicles, but they are not yet available.

items.name: case ready
items.desc: A response code that indicates you’re ready to provide a list of the user’s electric vehicles.

items.name: case success
items.desc: A response code that indicates you’re able to provide a list of the user’s electric vehicles.

items.name: case unspecified
items.desc: A response code that indicates the absence of a genuine response code.
